{"tid":276252,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"2013年：篤數造假的\"M血時報\"，有何公信力呢？","createTime":"2017-06-08T16:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T16:14:51.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80e71b0def671c1ccfc6cef2a68ca194561920e4","tid":276252,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:14:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://forum.memehk.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=35775\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.memehk.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D35775&d=uOAYi3c9FJurCftt%2FpsdATQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=43ece040\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.memehk.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=35775</a><br />\n2013-12-5 21:45:57<br />\n同一個網台節目，在線人數由一周前的22,516人，變為今天的301人，不用讀過統計分析，都睇得出是篤數造假，此網台以&quot;時報&quot; 命名，連在線人數都欺騙觀/聽眾，請問公信力何在呢？沒有公信力，如何辦報呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳秀慧 《與時並進玩遊戲》(《AM730》，2013年03月06日)：<br />\n網台節目《宅文化研究》辦Puzzle &amp; Dragons打機破關直播節目，同時在線人數最高峰達<strong>兩萬多人</strong>，突破網台界最高在線人數紀錄，在一直只著重論政節目的網台界引來佳話。當然佳話之餘亦引來流言蜚語，造數疑雲。But，想做個與時並進的人，Never judge what you don't understand。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://forum.memehk.com/data/attachment/forum/201312/05/214522nbv9cqyvmakb1aca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.memehk.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201312%2F05%2F214522nbv9cqyvmakb1aca.jpg&h=06bea63f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[<img src=\"http://forum.memehk.com/data/attachment/forum/201312/05/214550cu9bqctbd9cb9abq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.memehk.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201312%2F05%2F214550cu9bqctbd9cb9abq.jpg&h=9cdcb683&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}